text: Computer Vision, Section 001 - Announcements: Questions & Feedback for Guest Speaker Computer Vision, Section 001 - Announcements: Questions & Feedback for Guest Speaker Posted Thursday, November 20, 2025 10:34 PM EST Hi everyone, Thank you again for attending Yutong Bai’s guest talk today. If you have any follow-up questions or feedback for her, please feel free to share them using the form below: Google Form: https://forms.gle/pLizHW9up8uNMCrDA Your responses will be collected with your email so that Yutong can follow up if needed.
